data.description: Walk into this beautifully maintained home with LVP flooring, gorgeous kitchen counter tops, stainless steel appliances, and tiled tub/shower combos! Open floor plan, vaulted ceilings, and a screened in back porch! All of this on a corner lot with a full front porch and side entrance garage. A renovated home nestled in the SugarMill Community, that offers an inground pool, tennis court, children's park and more!
